<LegalPageLayout title="AI Disclosure" lastUpdated="December 5, 2025">
  <LegalSection title="My Commitment to Transparency">
    <p class="text-ink/80 dark:text-ink-dark/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">
      The Hobbinomicon is a one-person operation, and I believe in being transparent about how I create and maintain my content. This page explains my use of artificial intelligence tools and reaffirms my commitment to authentic, human-created content.
    </p>
  </LegalSection>

  <LegalSection title="What Is 100% Human-Created">
    <p class="text-ink/80 dark:text-ink-dark/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">
      <strong>All creative content on this website is created entirely by me:</strong>
    </p>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-8 text-ink/80 dark:text-ink-dark/80 leading-relaxed mb-4 space-y-2">
      <li><strong>Written Content:</strong> All blog posts, tutorials, guides, reviews, and articles are written by me. Every word, opinion, and idea comes from genuine human experience and creativity.</li>
      <li><strong>Images & Photography:</strong> All photographs, painted miniatures, and visual content are captured and created by me. No AI-generated images are used and will never be used.</li>
      <li><strong>Videos:</strong> All YouTube videos are filmed, edited, and produced by me.</li>
      <li><strong>Artwork:</strong> Any original artwork or illustrations are human-created.</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="text-ink/80 dark:text-ink-dark/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">
      When you read a tutorial, watch a video, or look at photos of my painted miniatures, you're experiencing genuine human creativity and craftsmanship.
    </p>
  </LegalSection>

  <LegalSection title="How I Use AI Tools">
    <p class="text-ink/80 dark:text-ink-dark/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">
      I do use AI tools in limited, behind-the-scenes capacities to help maintain and improve the website:
    </p>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-8 text-ink/80 dark:text-ink-dark/80 leading-relaxed mb-4 space-y-2">
      <li><strong>Website Development:</strong> I use vs code with AI coding assistants to help with programming tasks, debugging, and implementing new features on the website.</li>
      <li><strong>Site Organization:</strong> AI tools assit me with optimizing site performance, and maintaining the technical infrastructure.</li>
      <li><strong>Code Review:</strong> AI helps review and improve the codebase that powers this website.</li>
    </ul>
    
  </LegalSection>

  <LegalSection title="Why This Matters">
    <p class="text-ink/80 dark:text-ink-dark/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">
      <strong>All the writing, photos, and minis on this site come from me. Not AI.</strong> The takes are mine. The miniatures in the photos are stuff I actually built and painted. The reviews are based on games I've actually played.
    </p>
    <p class="text-ink/80 dark:text-ink-dark/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">
      A lot of the internet right now feels auto-generated. I want to be clear that this site isn't. If you're reading something here, a person wrote it. If you're looking at a peice of art, a human made it. 
    </p>
  </LegalSection>

